ActsAsI18nUi
============

An ActiveController extension to create a user interface to manage I18n
translations.

Requirements
============

Requires gems htmlentities and json:

	gem install htmlentities
	gem install json (or json-pure for windows)

Installation
============

script/plugin install git://github.com/horaci/acts-as-i18n-ui.git

Example
=======

class I18nController < ApplicationController
  acts_as_i18n_ui
end

